title: The Standard - Kenya : Eugene Wamalwa: I never said i would vie for Nairobi Gubernatorial seat
text:
KTN Faces Friday Briefing 
Did you ever wonder why water cabinet secretary Eugene Wamalwa suddenly went silent about his political ambitions? Well, will he or won’t he vie for the Nairobi governor’s seat as had been reported earlier? Our political reporter Duncan Khaemba delves into the woes of the CS who has finally broken his silence over the reasons he may be putting his political ambitions on hold.
